'''希腊法拉沛咖啡'''（Frappé coffee）是一种希臘[[冰咖啡|冰咖啡]]飲料，通常由[[即溶咖啡|即溶咖啡]]（基本上是[[雀巢咖啡|雀巢咖啡]]）、水、糖和牛奶制成<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|last=Mabbett|first=Terry|date=2007-10-01|title=Greece in an instant|url=https://www.thefreelibrary.com/Greece+in+an+instant%3A+Greece+is+often+regarded+as+the+cradle+of...-a0169924710|journal=Tea & Coffee Trade Journal|access-date=2020-05-24|via=The Free Library|archive-date=2021-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211127110836/https://www.thefreelibrary.com/Greece%20in%20an%20instant%3A%20Greece%20is%20often%20regarded%20as%20the%20cradle%20of...-a0169924710}}</ref>。咖啡的上面覆盖着[[奶泡|奶泡]]，有时还会加入[[冰块|冰块]]，适合在[[夏季|夏季]]饮用。

